Package: aws.ecx
Title: Communicating with Amazon Web Services(AWS) Elastic Compute Cloud(EC2) and Elastic Container Service(ECS) using AWS REST APIs
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Jiefei",
           family = "Wang",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "szwjf08@gmail.com")
Description: 
    The package provides the functions for communicating with AWS EC2 and ECS.
    The functions will have the prefix `ecs_` or `ec2_` depending on the class 
    of the API. The request will be sent via the REST APIs and the parameters are
    given by the function argument. The credentials can be set via `aws_set_credentials`.
